msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Ma tha thu taobh a-muigh na Stàitean Aonaichte, mholamaid NOWPayments "
"(cumhaich cuid as lùb, dìreach gu dho shlighe). Ma tha thu ann am Stàitean "
"Aonaichte, tha Stripe Crypto cuideachd na roghainn. Faodaidh tu barrachd "
"seirbheisean a chur air adhart agus leigeas do luchd-tadhail a thaghadh!"

