msgstr "Cuir mo charaid in fìn gun a’ chèinear agaibh"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Eadar-uirre uaisle, saor an-tasgaidh is pàigheadh a leigeas do luchd-turadh "
"taic a thoirt seachad tro càrd àrdtean no criptò-bhrùthadh (Quai). Gun "
"fhìor-mhothaich mìosail, gun chrùbadh a-steach de dhlùth-phròiseas – dìreach"
" a’ bhuis agad is seirbheisean saor."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Tha cuid de bhrabhsaran a’ cur bacadh air scriptean treas-phàrtaidh airson "
"prìobhaideachd. Leigidh an proxy seo scriptean a luchdadh tro do "
"fhrithealaiche fhèin airson na bacadh a thìreachadh."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Faodaidh tu cothromachadh URL-annan scriptean gu h-ìobairt ma dh’ atharraich"
" na URL-annan bunaiteach no ma tha thu airson CDN eadar-dhealaichte a "
"chleachdadh."

